35:04.631 --> 35:06.299
<i>Uh, wait.</i>
<i>What about my pancakes?</i>

35:06.299 --> 35:07.698
<i>Uh, wait.</i>
<i>What about my pancakes?</i>

35:07.801 --> 35:09.462
