35:12.772 --> 35:15.036
Now how could beauty be so evil?

35:16.843 --> 35:21.507
I've been stung so many times,
I have immunity.

35:21.614 --> 35:23.809
They barely even hurt me.

35:23.917 --> 35:27.683
But since you don't, you need
to know beeyard etiquette.

35:27.787 --> 35:31.018
- Beeyard etiquette?
- You see...

35:31.124 --> 35:33.115
