41:26.915 --> 41:28.815
Ooh.

41:35.457 --> 41:37.357
- Mmm, mmm.
- Just put it in.

41:37.459 --> 41:40.292
Miss August, you know
I got stung today, right?

41:40.395 --> 41:42.295
