41:52.273 --> 41:54.298
No, I'm telling you that
they don't intend on voting.

41:54.409 --> 41:56.400
<i>But you gotta see it from the other side.</i>

41:56.511 --> 41:59.810
<i>The time is right</i>

41:59.914 --> 42:03.941
<i>I'm gonna pack my bags</i>

